with values as (
select
  ts,
  jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.rh')::real as val
FROM
  telem
where
  device = 'rhtweeter'
  and ts between $__timeFrom()
  AND $__timeTo()
order by
  ts asc
)
select 
  ts,
  val as rhtweeter
from values;

with temps as
(select
  ts,
  jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.temps[0]')::real as temp1,
  jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.temps[1]')::real as temp2
FROM
  telem
where
  device = 'temprack'
  and ec = 'telem_temps'
  and ts between $__timeFrom()
  AND $__timeTo()
) select * FROM temps
where temp1 > 0 and temp2 > 0
order by
  ts asc;

with camtemps as (
select
  ts,
  jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.tempCtrl.temp')::real as temp,
  jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.tempCtrl.setpt')::real as setpt
  -- ,
  -- jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.temps[1]')::real as temp2
FROM
  telem
where
  ec = 'telem_stdcam'
  and device = 'camsci1'
  and ts between $__timeFrom()
  AND $__timeTo()
order by
  ts asc
)
select 
  ts,
  setpt as camsci1_setpt,
  case when temp = -999 then null else temp end as camsci1_temp
from camtemps;

select
  ts,
  case when jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.ccd')::real != -999 then jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.ccd')::real else null end as ccd,
  case when jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.cpu')::real != -999 then jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.cpu')::real else null end as cpu,
  case when jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.water')::real != -999 then jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.water')::real else null end as water
  -- ,
  -- jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.temps[1]')::real as temp2
FROM
  telem
where
  ec = 'ocam_temps'
  and device = 'camwfs'
  and ts between $__timeFrom()
  AND $__timeTo()
order by
  ts asc;

select
  ts,
  case when jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.ccd')::real != -999 then jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.ccd')::real else null end as ccd,

  case when jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.water')::real != -999 then jsonb_path_query_first(msg, '$.water')::real else null end as water
